    <entry>
      <title>C++构造函数与析构函数</title>
      <link href="2020/12/16/C-%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8E%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0/"/>
      <url>2020/12/16/C-%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0%E4%B8%8E%E6%9E%90%E6%9E%84%E5%87%BD%E6%95%B0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>本篇文章谈一谈C++中的各种构造函数和析构函数</p></blockquote><h2 id="构造函数"><a href="#构造函数" class="headerlink" title="构造函数"></a>构造函数</h2><p>构造函数在一个对象被创建的时候起作用,一个类可以有多个构造函数，只要编译器能够区分即可，主要有编译器的默认构造函数，自己编写的带参数或者无参构造函数，复制构造函数以及类型转换转换构造函数。</p><p>首先先声明一个class</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>类的成员就三个。</p><h3 id="默认构造函数"><a href="#默认构造函数" class="headerlink" title="默认构造函数"></a>默认构造函数</h3><p>如果找不到构造函数，那么编译器为该类添加一个无参构造函数，该函数什么事情都不做。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Player player;     <span class="comment">// 此处调用默认的无参构造函数  什么都不做</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="自己编写无参构造函数"><a href="#自己编写无参构造函数" class="headerlink" title="自己编写无参构造函数"></a>自己编写无参构造函数</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">  Player();      <span class="comment">// 声明一个无参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;我是一个无参构造函数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Player player;     <span class="comment">// 调用无参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="自己编写的带参数的构造函数"><a href="#自己编写的带参数的构造函数" class="headerlink" title="自己编写的带参数的构造函数"></a>自己编写的带参数的构造函数</h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">  Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y);      <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;我是一个有参构造函数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  x = _x;</span><br><span class="line">  y = _y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Player <span class="title">player</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>)</span></span>;     <span class="comment">// 调用有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">  LOG(player.x);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(player.y);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 也可以从堆中new一个对象；</span></span><br><span class="line">  Player *pplayer = <span class="keyword">new</span> Player(<span class="number">5</span>,<span class="number">6</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(pplayer-&gt;x);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(pplayer-&gt;y);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">delete</span> pplayer;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出如下：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="构造函数在数组中的应用"><a href="#构造函数在数组中的应用" class="headerlink" title="构造函数在数组中的应用"></a>构造函数在数组中的应用</h3><p>这里为了体现一些特性，写出一些构造函数的重载</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 声明3个构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    Player();                    <span class="comment">// 无参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y);      <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _speed);          <span class="comment">// 参数表不同</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;我是一个有参构造函数（int， int）&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  x = _x;</span><br><span class="line">  y = _y;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _speed)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;我是一个有参构造函数（int）&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  speed = _speed;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;我是一个无参构造函数&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 对于单个参数的构造函数的使用</span></span><br><span class="line">  Player array1[<span class="number">2</span>];</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-1&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Player array2[<span class="number">2</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-2&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Player array3[<span class="number">2</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-3&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Player *array4 = <span class="keyword">new</span> Player[<span class="number">2</span>];</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">delete</span> [] array4;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-4&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">// 对含有多个参数的构造函数的使用</span></span><br><span class="line">  Player array5[<span class="number">3</span>] = &#123;<span class="number">1</span>, Player(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">5</span>)&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-5&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  Player *array6[<span class="number">3</span>] = &#123;<span class="keyword">new</span> Player(<span class="number">4</span>),<span class="keyword">new</span> Player(<span class="number">6</span>,<span class="number">7</span>)&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">delete</span> array6[<span class="number">0</span>];</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">delete</span> array6[<span class="number">1</span>];</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;STEP-6&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该端程序的执行结果如下，可以对照代码理解每一个构造函数被调用的情况，着重讲一下最后一种情况，也就是array6[3], 为什么只调用了两次构造函数。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">STEP-1</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int）</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int）</span><br><span class="line">STEP-2</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int）</span><br><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">STEP-3</span><br><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">STEP-4</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int）</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int， int）</span><br><span class="line">我是一个无参构造函数</span><br><span class="line">STEP-5</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int）</span><br><span class="line">我是一个有参构造函数（int， int）</span><br><span class="line">STEP-6</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>构造函数只在一个对象被创建的时候被调用，虽然array6[3]有3个元素，但是只给前两个元素调用的new，也就是只创建了两个对象。</p><h3 id="复制构造函数"><a href="#复制构造函数" class="headerlink" title="复制构造函数"></a>复制构造函数</h3><h4 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h4><p>复制构造函数是构造函数的一种，只有一个参数，参数类型是对本类的引用，如果设计者不编写复制构造函数，编译器会自动生成复制构造函数，大多数情况其作用是实现从源对象到目标对象的逐个字节的拷贝。</p><p>下面是一个复制构造函数的例子，还是以Player类为例。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">    Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y,<span class="keyword">int</span> _speed);      <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 列表初始化</span></span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x,<span class="keyword">int</span> _y, <span class="keyword">int</span> _speed):x(_x),y(_y),speed(_speed)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Player <span class="title">p1</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Player <span class="title">p2</span><span class="params">(p1)</span></span>;      <span class="comment">// 用复制构造函数初始化p2</span></span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.x);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.y);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.speed);      <span class="comment">// 输出和p1相同  3, 4, 5</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>只有编译器自动生成的默认复制构造函数的参数和p1匹配，因此，p2就是以p1为参数，调用默认复制构造函数进行初始化的，初始化的结果是p2成了p1的复制品。</p><p>如果编写了自己的复制构造函数，那么默认的复制构造函数就不存在了。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">    Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y,<span class="keyword">int</span> _speed);      <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">    Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp; p);               <span class="comment">// 声明复制构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 列表初始化</span></span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x,<span class="keyword">int</span> _y, <span class="keyword">int</span> _speed):x(_x),y(_y),speed(_speed)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 复制构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp; p)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  x = p.x; y = p.y; speed = p.speed;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;复制构造函数被调用&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Player <span class="title">p1</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">3</span>,<span class="number">4</span>,<span class="number">5</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Player <span class="title">p2</span><span class="params">(p1)</span></span>;      <span class="comment">// 用复制构造函数初始化p2</span></span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.x);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.y);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p2.speed);      </span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出如下，可以看到自己写的复制构造函数被调用了。</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">复制构造函数被调用</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="复制构造函数被调用的时机"><a href="#复制构造函数被调用的时机" class="headerlink" title="复制构造函数被调用的时机"></a>复制构造函数被调用的时机</h4><p>主要有三种情况</p><ol><li><p><strong>当用一个对象取初始化同类的另一个对象时，会引发复制构造函数被调用</strong>。如下两行语句都会引发复制构造函数取初始化p2</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Player p2(p1);</span><br><span class="line">Player p2&#x3D;p1;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意第二行是初始化不是赋值。 </p></li><li><p><strong>如果一个函数的参数是类Player的对象，那么当函数被调用需要传入实参的时候，该实参使用复制构造函数去初始化的</strong>。例子：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span> &#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="keyword">public</span>: </span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">   Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y,<span class="keyword">int</span> _speed);      <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">   Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp; p);               <span class="comment">// 声明复制构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line"> &#125;;</span><br><span class="line"> Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x,<span class="keyword">int</span> _y, <span class="keyword">int</span> _speed):x(_x),y(_y),speed(_speed)&#123; &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> Player::Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp; p)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   x = p.x; y = p.y; speed = p.speed;</span><br><span class="line">   LOG(<span class="string">&quot;复制构造函数被调用&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">Fun</span><span class="params">(Player p)</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   LOG(<span class="string">&quot;调用Fun&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br><span class="line"> <span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">   <span class="function">Player <span class="title">p</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">2</span>,<span class="number">3</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">   Fun(p);</span><br><span class="line"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序运行结果：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">复制构造函数被调用</span><br><span class="line">调用Fun</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当然，如果函数的参数是引用的时候，就不存在复制构造函数被调用，因为这时候不需要构造一个对象。</p></li><li><p>如果函数的返回值是类Player的对象，则函数返回时，类Player的复制构造函数被调用，也就是<strong>作为函数返回值的对象是用复制构造函数初始化的</strong>。举例：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">// 声明class Player</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Player</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">int</span> x, y;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">int</span> speed;</span><br><span class="line">  Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y, <span class="keyword">int</span> _speed); <span class="comment">// 声明一个有参构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">  Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp;p);            <span class="comment">// 声明复制构造函数</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">int</span> _x, <span class="keyword">int</span> _y, <span class="keyword">int</span> _speed) : x(_x), y(_y), speed(_speed) &#123;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">Player::Player(<span class="keyword">const</span> Player &amp;p)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  x = p.x;</span><br><span class="line">  y = p.y;</span><br><span class="line">  speed = p.speed;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;复制构造函数被调用&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Player <span class="title">p</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>, <span class="number">7</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">Player <span class="title">Fun</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(<span class="string">&quot;调用Fun&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> p;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  Player p = Fun();</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p.x);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p.y);</span><br><span class="line">  LOG(p.speed);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输出结果如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">调用Fun</span><br><span class="line">复制构造函数被调用</span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">5</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">6</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="number">7</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="类型转换构造函数"><a href="#类型转换构造函数" class="headerlink" title="类型转换构造函数"></a>类型转换构造函数</h3><p>除了复制构造函数之外，只有一个参数的构造函数一般都可以成为类型转换构造函数，因为这样的构造函数能够起到类型自动转换的作用。比如：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">define</span> LOG(x) std::cout &lt;&lt; x &lt;&lt; std::endl</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Complex</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">double</span> real, imag;</span><br><span class="line">    Complex(<span class="keyword">int</span> i)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      LOG(<span class="string">&quot;IntConstructor called&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">      real = i; imag = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    Complex(<span class="keyword">double</span> r, <span class="keyword">double</span> i)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      real = r; imag = i;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">Complex <span class="title">c1</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">7</span>,<span class="number">8</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">  Complex c2 = <span class="number">12</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  c1 = <span class="number">9</span>;       <span class="comment">// 9被自动转换成一个临时Complex对象;</span></span><br><span class="line">  LOG(c1.real&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>&lt;&lt;c1.imag);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>程序的输出结果：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">IntConstructor called</span><br><span class="line">IntConstructor called</span><br><span class="line">9,0</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="析构函数"><a href="#析构函数" class="headerlink" title="析构函数"></a>析构函数</h2><p>析构函数在对象消亡时被自动调用，可以定义在对象消亡前做善后工作。</p><p>一个类有且只有一个析构函数，他的名字和类名相同但是前面要加上”～“，没有参数和返回值，如果没有自己写析构函数，那么编译器自动生成。举例</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="meta-keyword">include</span> <span class="meta-string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">String</span>&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">private</span>: </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">char</span> *p;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">public</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    String(<span class="keyword">int</span> n);</span><br><span class="line">    ~String();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br><span class="line">String::String(<span class="keyword">int</span> n)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  p = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="keyword">char</span>[n];</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line">String::~String()&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">cout</span> &lt;&lt; <span class="string">&quot;析构函数被调用&quot;</span> &lt;&lt;<span class="built_in">std</span>::<span class="built_in">endl</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">delete</span> [] p;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="function">String <span class="title">s</span><span class="params">(<span class="number">100</span>)</span></span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>上面的String类，成员变量p指向动态分配的一片存储空间，分配在构造函数中进行，而空间的释放在析构函数中进行，这样在其他地方就不用考虑空间释放的事情了，上述程序在结束之前也就是s消亡之前，自动调用析构函数，释放p指向的空间。</p><p>运行结果:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">析构函数被调用</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="祝所有人心想事成"><a href="#祝所有人心想事成" class="headerlink" title="祝所有人心想事成"></a>祝所有人心想事成</h2>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>机器学习基本环境搭建</title>
      <link href="2020/12/15/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/"/>
      <url>2020/12/15/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>操作系统环境为manjaro Linux</p></blockquote><h2 id="安装Miniconda"><a href="#安装Miniconda" class="headerlink" title="安装Miniconda"></a>安装Miniconda</h2><p>从官网下载miniconda，这里使用python3.8版本(<a href="https://docs.conda.io/en/latest/miniconda.html" title="miniconda 下载">下载地址</a>)，这里我选择的是<a href="https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh">Miniconda3 Linux 64-bit</a>。</p><p>打开终端，进入文件保存的目录，执行：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sh Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh    <span class="comment"># 换成你自己的文件名</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>首先协议是否同意，输入<code>yes</code>回车，然后一路默认选项，到了最后有一个是否写入环境变量，这里输入<code>yes</code>然后回车。重新打开终端，可以看到最左侧有一个<code>(base)</code>的字样，那么说明安装成功了。</p><h2 id="conda的基本操作"><a href="#conda的基本操作" class="headerlink" title="conda的基本操作"></a>conda的基本操作</h2><h3 id="版本和帮助"><a href="#版本和帮助" class="headerlink" title="版本和帮助"></a>版本和帮助</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda --version           <span class="comment"># 获取版本号</span></span><br><span class="line">conda --<span class="built_in">help</span>              <span class="comment"># 获取帮助</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="环境管理"><a href="#环境管理" class="headerlink" title="环境管理"></a>环境管理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda env -h              <span class="comment"># 查看环境管理的全部命令</span></span><br><span class="line">conda create --name &#123;env_name&#125;   <span class="comment"># 创建环境，将&#123;env_name&#125;换成自己的名字</span></span><br><span class="line">conda create --name &#123;env_name&#125; python=3.6 numpy scipy <span class="comment"># 同时制定python版本和包</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">conda info --envs         <span class="comment"># 列举所有环境</span></span><br><span class="line">conda env list            <span class="comment"># 同上</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">activate &#123;env_name&#125;       <span class="comment"># 激活环境</span></span><br><span class="line">deactivate                <span class="comment"># 退出当前环境</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">conda create --name &#123;new__env_name&#125; --<span class="built_in">clone</span> &#123;old_env_name&#125;    <span class="comment"># 复制环境</span></span><br><span class="line">conda remove --name &#123;env_name&#125; --all        <span class="comment"># 删除环境</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="包管理"><a href="#包管理" class="headerlink" title="包管理"></a>包管理</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda list                <span class="comment"># 列举当前活跃环境所有的包</span></span><br><span class="line">conda list -n &#123;env_name&#125;  <span class="comment">#列举制定环境下的包</span></span><br><span class="line">conda install &#123;package_name&#125;                <span class="comment"># 为当前环境安装包</span></span><br><span class="line">conda install -n &#123;env_name&#125; &#123;package_name&#125;  <span class="comment"># 为某个环境安装包</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果conda太慢了，也可以使用pip来安装包，首先修改pip源为清华源</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install pip -U     <span class="comment"># 更新pip</span></span><br><span class="line">pip config <span class="built_in">set</span> global.index-url https://pypi.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/simple</span><br><span class="line">pip install &#123;package_name&#125;                <span class="comment"># 为当前环境安装包</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="安装基本包"><a href="#安装基本包" class="headerlink" title="安装基本包"></a>安装基本包</h2><h3 id="常用包列表"><a href="#常用包列表" class="headerlink" title="常用包列表"></a>常用包列表</h3><p>这里安装一些常用的包和pytorch，等需要的时候可以补充安装，pytorch等会安装</p><ul><li>matplotlib</li><li>numpy</li><li>pandas</li><li>jupyter</li><li>seaborn(基于matplotlib的画图库)</li><li>Scikit-Learn</li><li>scipy</li><li>pytorch</li></ul><h3 id="新建环境"><a href="#新建环境" class="headerlink" title="新建环境"></a>新建环境</h3><p>使用conda新建一个环境，这里我取名为<code>withtorch</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda create --name withtorch    <span class="comment"># 新建环境</span></span><br><span class="line">conda activate withtorch          <span class="comment"># 激活环境</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装基本包-1"><a href="#安装基本包-1" class="headerlink" title="安装基本包"></a>安装基本包</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># pytorch单独安装</span></span><br><span class="line">conda install matplotlib numpy pandas jupyter seaborn scikit-learn scipy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="安装pytorch"><a href="#安装pytorch" class="headerlink" title="安装pytorch"></a>安装pytorch</h3><p>pytorch的<a href="https://pytorch.org/get-started/locally/">官网</a>给了很好的安装指令，对照自己的情况选择即可,由于我没有cuda，所以我的配置如下：</p><img src="/2020/12/15/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/pytorch.webp" class="" title="pytorch安装" alt="pytorch安装"><p>输入命令：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">conda install pytorch torchvision torchaudio cpuonly -c pytorch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此，基本上要用的包都安装完毕，可以在终端验证</p><img src="/2020/12/15/%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/verify.webp" class="" title="验证安装" alt="验证安装"><hr><p><strong>祝所有人心想事成</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
      <categories>
          
          <category> 学习 </category>
          
